About us

Community

We are a community of developers who volunteer their time and expertise to build open source software for the greater good, with a shared vision of making a positive impact on the world through technology. Our diverse and talented community spans across different domains and backgrounds, united by our passion for coding and the desire to contribute to meaningful projects.

Passion

As part of our commitment to fostering continuous learning and growth, we provide a wealth of resources to support your software development journey. Our focus is on project-based learning, enabling you to gain hands-on experience and practical skills that are directly applicable to real-world scenarios. Through tutorials, documentation, and interactive workshops, we aim to equip you with the tools and knowledge needed to excel in the open source software development community.

Educate

We provide resources to help you learn software development that is orientated on project based learning

Problem Solve

We believe that open source software has the power to solve some of the world's biggest problems, and we're committed to using our skills to make that happen

); } export default AboutSection;
